data.description: Happy House! Happy You!  Thiis beautiful home has had a recent price improvement and the HVAC was recently cleaned and serviced.  All is GOOD!  This  all brick ranch home has what it takes....all new paint, new carpet in the primary bedroom, new light fixtures, newly painted kitchen cabinets, new sliding door with built in blinds and new crown moulding. This home is sparkling clean to include the privacy fenced yard. Pressure washed throughout.  Great level yard with plenty of room to run, play or just enjoy your private wooded oasis. Split bedroom plan, large rooms throughout.  Take a look and call 941 Willowick....HOME!
